---
// AgentArchitecture.astro — 3-layer agent architecture diagram
---

<div class="aa-wrap">
  <h3 class="aa-title">The Architecture: 3 Layers of Every Agent</h3>
  <p class="aa-sub">Brain picks the action. Hands do the work. Guardrails keep it safe.</p>

  <div class="aa-layers">
    <div class="aa-layer aa-layer--1">
      <div class="aa-layer-header">
        <div class="aa-layer-badge aa-lb--purple">🧠</div>
        <div class="aa-layer-info">
          <span class="aa-layer-name">The Brain — LLM + System Prompt</span>
          <span class="aa-layer-role">Decides what to do next</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="aa-layer-body">
        <div class="aa-layer-items">
          <span class="aa-item">System prompt with role + rules</span>
          <span class="aa-item">Conversation history</span>
          <span class="aa-item">Tool definitions (function schemas)</span>
          <span class="aa-item">ReAct reasoning pattern</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="aa-connector">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 20 24"><path d="M10 0v24" stroke="#334155" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/><path d="M5 18l5 6 5-6" fill="#334155"/></svg>
    </div>

    <div class="aa-layer aa-layer--2">
      <div class="aa-layer-header">
        <div class="aa-layer-badge aa-lb--green">🔧</div>
        <div class="aa-layer-info">
          <span class="aa-layer-name">The Hands — Tools + APIs</span>
          <span class="aa-layer-role">Executes actions in the real world</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="aa-layer-body">
        <div class="aa-tool-grid">
          <div class="aa-tool">
            <span class="aa-tool-icon">🔍</span>
            <span class="aa-tool-name">Search</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aa-tool">
            <span class="aa-tool-icon">🌐</span>
            <span class="aa-tool-name">API Call</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aa-tool">
            <span class="aa-tool-icon">💻</span>
            <span class="aa-tool-name">Code Run</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aa-tool">
            <span class="aa-tool-icon">🗄️</span>
            <span class="aa-tool-name">Database</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aa-tool">
            <span class="aa-tool-icon">📧</span>
            <span class="aa-tool-name">Email</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aa-tool">
            <span class="aa-tool-icon">📁</span>
            <span class="aa-tool-name">Files</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="aa-connector">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 20 24"><path d="M10 0v24" stroke="#334155" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/><path d="M5 18l5 6 5-6" fill="#334155"/></svg>
    </div>

    <div class="aa-layer aa-layer--3">
      <div class="aa-layer-header">
        <div class="aa-layer-badge aa-lb--red">🛡️</div>
        <div class="aa-layer-info">
          <span class="aa-layer-name">The Guardrails — Safety + Limits</span>
          <span class="aa-layer-role">Prevents damage and runaway costs</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="aa-layer-body">
        <div class="aa-layer-items aa-items--red">
          <span class="aa-item">Max loop iterations (prevent infinite loops)</span>
          <span class="aa-item">Token budget per request</span>
          <span class="aa-item">Tool permission allowlist</span>
          <span class="aa-item">Human-in-the-loop for destructive actions</span>
          <span class="aa-item">Output validation and content filtering</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .aa-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .aa-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .aa-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .aa-layers { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0; }

  .aa-layer {
    width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #334155; overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0; animation: aaIn 0.5s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .aa-layer--1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .aa-layer--2 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .aa-layer--3 { animation-delay: 1.0s; }

  .aa-layer-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
  .aa-layer-badge { font-size: 1.2rem; width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .aa-lb--purple { background: rgba(129,140,248,0.1); }
  .aa-lb--green { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.1); }
  .aa-lb--red { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); }

  .aa-layer-name { display: block; color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.82rem; }
  .aa-layer-role { display: block; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.65rem; font-family: monospace; margin-top: 2px; }

  .aa-layer-body { padding: 12px 16px; }

  .aa-layer-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .aa-item {
    color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.7rem; padding-left: 12px; position: relative; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .aa-item::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #818cf8; font-size: 0.6rem; }
  .aa-items--red .aa-item::before { color: #f87171; }

  .aa-tool-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
  .aa-tool {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(74,222,128,0.04); border: 1px solid #4ade8015;
  }
  .aa-tool-icon { font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .aa-tool-name { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.65rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .aa-connector { width: 20px; height: 24px; }

  @keyframes aaIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
</style>
